NCDHC Consent Category

http://hl7.org.au/fhir/ch/v1/ValueSet/ncdhc-consent-category-1

National Children Digital Health Collaborative - Consent Category - this value set represents the consent status applicable to the creation and operation of the Child Digital Health Record and Digital Pregnancy Health Record initiatives for the National Digital Health Collaborative.
